m spanning from September to December.\n      </p>\n      \n      <div style={{ display: 'grid', gap: '1rem', marginTop: '2rem' }}>\n        <div style={{ padding: '1rem', border: '1px solid var(--border)', borderRadius: 'var(--radius)' }}>\n          <h2>September: Kinematics & Dynamics</h2>\n          <p>Interactive Build: \"Drag Force Differential\" — FBD creation to variable separation.</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div style={{ padding: '1rem', border: '1px solid var(--border)', borderRadius: 'var(--radius)' }}>\n          <h2>October: Energy & Momentum</h2>\n          <p>Interactive Build: \"Energy Landscape\" — deriving F = -dU/dx and 2D collision logic trees.</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div style={{ padding: '1rem', border: '1px solid var(--border)', borderRadius: 'var(--radius)' }}>\n          <h2>November: Rotational Mechanics</h2>\n          <p>Interactive Build: \"Rolling Without Slipping\" decision matrices and cross-product trainers.</p>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div style={{ padding: '1rem', border: '1px solid var(--border)', borderRadius: 'var(--radius)' }}>\n          <h2>December: Gravitation & Oscillations</h2>\n          <p>Interactive Build: Physical pendulum derivation scaffolding.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </main>\n  );\n}\n","usedDeprecatedRules":[]},{"filePath":"C:\\Users\\samue\\OneDrive\\Desktop\\Projects\\Phyne\\src\\app\\page.tsx","messages":[{"ruleId":"@typescript-eslint/no-unused-vars","severity":1,"message":"'Link' is defined but never used.","line":4,"column":8,"nodeType":"Identifier","messageId":"unusedVar","endLine":4,"endColumn":12,"suggestions":[{"messageId":"removeUnusedImportDeclaration","data":{"varName":"Link"},"fix":{"range":[67,97],"text":""},"desc":"Remove unused import declaration."}]},{"ruleId":"react-hooks/set-state-in-effect","severity":2,"message":"Error: Calling setState synchronously within an effect can trigger cascading renders\n\nEffects are intended to synchronize sta